planned $250 million. The debentures, which are noncallable
for two years, may be put back to the company in the fifth
and 10th years. Rated single-A-3 by Moody's and single-A-plus
by S&amp;P, the issue will be sold through underwriters led by
First Boston Corp.
   AMR Corp. -- $100 million of debentures, due June 15,
